{"type":"message","id":"e0f9a357","parentId":"00726075","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:00:22.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"两个账号都需要重新登录！问题是浏览器 persistent context 中保存的登录状态已过期。\n\n解决方案：\n1. 手动登录两个账号（需要用户干预）\n2. 使用 cookies 文件恢复登录\n\n由于脚本没有实现 cookies 恢复功能，需要先手动登录或更新脚本。\n\n让我先尝试使用 cookies 文件来恢复登录状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**发现问题：两个番茄账号的登录状态都已失效，需要重新登录。**\n\n让我尝试用 cookies 文件恢复登录：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rimypsbcbc2r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/auto-scripts && node -e \"\nconst { chromium } = require('playwright');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n\nasync function restoreAndLogin(accountNum) {\n  const browserDir = 'browser/fanqie_account_' + accountNum;\n  const cookieFile = '/workspace/projects/cookies-accounts/fanqie-20260314-' + (accountNum === 1 ? '030709' : '112322') + '.json';\n  \n  console.log('账号' + accountNum + ':');\n  console.log('  浏览器目录:', browserDir);\n  console.log('  Cookies文件:', cookieFile);\n  console.log('  文件存在:', fs.existsSync(cookieFile));\n  \n  if (!fs.existsSync(cookieFile)) {\n    console.log('  ✗ Cookies文件不存在');\n    return;\n  }\n  \n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(cookieFile, 'utf-8')).cookies;\n  console.log('  Cookies数量:', cookies?.length);\n  \n  const browser = await chromium.launchPersistentContext(browserDir, {\n    headless: false, channel: 'chrome', args: ['--no-sandbox']\n  });\n  const page = browser.pages()[0];\n  \n  // 添加 cookies\n  await page.context().addCookies(cookies);\n  \n  // 访问页面\n  await page.goto('https://fanqienovel.com/main/writer/book-manage', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded' });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  \n  console.log('  页面标题:', await page.title());\n  const html = await page.content();\n  console.log('  登录成功?', !html.includes('登录/注册') ? 'yes' : 'no');\n  \n  await browser.close();\n}\n\nrestoreAndLogin(1);\n\" 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":92,"output":579,"cacheRead":45821,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46492,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773806413949}}
