{"type":"message","id":"9b1eb2a5","parentId":"334dcd72","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:00:38.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！使用 cookies 文件可以成功恢复登录。现在我需要更新脚本，让它在打开番茄页面之前先加载 cookies。\n\n但这需要修改代码，这不是 cron 任务应该做的事情。让我先手动为两个账号恢复登录状态，然后重新运行发布脚本。\n\n实际上，我可以写一个临时脚本来为两个账号恢复登录，然后再运行发布脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Cookies 可以恢复登录。让我为两个账号恢复登录状态，然后再运行发布脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lff9hdj3y70k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/auto-scripts && node -e \"\nconst { chromium } = require('playwright');\nconst fs = require('fs');\n\nasync function restoreLogin(accountNum) {\n  const browserDir = 'browser/fanqie_account_' + accountNum;\n  const cookieFile = '/workspace/projects/cookies-accounts/fanqie-20260314-' + (accountNum === 1 ? '030709' : '112322') + '.json';\n  \n  console.log('恢复账号' + accountNum + '登录状态...');\n  \n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(cookieFile, 'utf-8')).cookies;\n  \n  const browser = await chromium.launchPersistentContext(browserDir, {\n    headless: false, channel: 'chrome', args: ['--no-sandbox']\n  });\n  const page = browser.pages()[0];\n  \n  await page.context().addCookies(cookies);\n  await page.goto('https://fanqienovel.com/main/writer/book-manage', { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded' });\n  await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n  \n  console.log('账号' + accountNum + '登录状态已恢复');\n  await browser.close();\n}\n\n(async () => {\n  await restoreLogin(1);\n  await restoreLogin(2);\n  console.log('✓ 所有账号登录状态已恢复');\n})();\n\" 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":185,"output":482,"cacheRead":46333,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773806431244}}
